description: Masters of Time: Independent Watchmakers- Series 1 Technology Documentary hosted by Michael Rhys, published by NHK in 2016 - English narration http://docuwiki.net/images/5/5d/Masters-of-Time-Independent-Watchmakers-Series-1-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ Masters Of Time: Independent Watchmakers- Series 1 The world's elite independent watchmakers are incredibly passionate about watch making from design to assembly, delicately bringing together hundreds of minuscule parts all by hand. The price for one such truly artistic timepiece can fetch up to hundreds of thousands of dollars. 3) Christiaan van der Klaauw & Beat Haldimann In a wry and timely commentary on the current rage for high-tech gadgets, this program spotlights the unusual skill, patience and passion underlying the "old-fashioned" art of handmade watches.
